3309 NE 169th ⚡Eastern Shores ⚡Offered for $4,275,000 ⚡Located in the exclusive community of Eastern Shores, prime location, 3 homes off open water, this turnkey gem combines Traditional design with Florida paradise-living. 🌴 The great room leads to a sunny, gourmet kitchen and two separate dining areas, surrounded by floor-to-ceiling windows and soaring ceilings allowing for beautiful natural light and open water views of Maul Lake. 🌊 The master suite is complete with a custom walk-in closet, a large soaking tub, a walk-in shower, and views of the outdoor space from your private balcony. All four upstairs bedrooms also feature en-suite bathrooms. 🛏️ This entertainer's dream boasts a spacious backyard sitting upon 85 ft of water with a fully equipped dock, pool, spa, a covered summer kitchen and multiple seating areas for dining and entertaining 😍
-

#easternshores #easternshoresrealestate #houses #homes #listing #listed #dreamhome #luxuryrealestate #florida
